{"tid":2133690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台會考慮在今晚發出三號強風信號 31/7","createTime":"2020-07-31T08:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T10:06:47.000Z","uid":27047,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4a24f9ba56c5c194be0f6242b7c932e68f2ab17b","tid":2133690,"uid":27047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:48:23.000Z","msg":"位於南海中北部的季風低壓正逐漸增強，一個熱帶氣旋似乎在形成中。天文台會考慮在今晚發出三號強風信號，並取消強烈季候風信號。預料該低壓區在星期六及星期日移向海南島至北部灣一帶，華南沿岸風勢頗大，有狂風大驟雨及雷暴，海面有大浪及湧浪。市民應該遠離岸邊及停止所有水上活動。<br />\n<br />\n於 2020 年 7 月 31 日 16 時 45 分 發 出"},{"pid":"a907cde7e1ce87a88cd15c7aba8757013b52cfbb","tid":2133690,"uid":27047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:51:53.000Z","msg":"大交合<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1141b0df3323c9d0616308c095d5f263e06b48d6","tid":2133690,"uid":218731,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:55:27.000Z","msg":"WFH 嗰啲如果掛八字波使唔使照開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77749d1dc4cb8b9d765f2cad9c912036dd41dc8e","tid":2133690,"uid":215734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1141b0df3323c9d0616308c095d5f263e06b48d6","tid":2133690,"uid":218731,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:55:27.000Z","msg":"WFH 嗰啲如果掛八字波使唔使照開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:55:49.000Z","msg":"留在安全地方開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae7f1f72eb28605943b4d9c1bf00fb7e41fcc0b","tid":2133690,"uid":27047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77749d1dc4cb8b9d765f2cad9c912036dd41dc8e","tid":2133690,"uid":215734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1141b0df3323c9d0616308c095d5f263e06b48d6","tid":2133690,"uid":218731,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:55:27.000Z","msg":"WFH 嗰啲如果掛八